Invocation Name: mito phone unofficial
des:
Send text messages to any number in the United States from your Twilio Account.

Currently the text messages are being sent using my own number provided by Twilio. Users who have a Twilio Account can use this skill with their Twilio Account Information (such as Twillo specified number) to send the texts.

Note: The skill is not sponsored or endorsed by PT Maju Express Indonesia.
